The city of lions. Beaulieu-sur-Dordogne. The war starts. Drole de guerre.
Going to work. Going to school. Fleeing from village to village. Playing cat
and mouse. The second landing. Return to Beaulieu. Return to Paris. Joining the
boyscouts. Learning languages. Israel becomes independent. Arrival in Haifa.
Kalay high school. Military training. The Hebrew Technion in Haifa. Relativity.
Asher Peres. Metallurgy. Return to France. Escape from jail. Aviva.